job.body:
Total vacancies:1500

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Welder (Gas & Electric)-100
  • Fitter-800
  • Electrician-500
  • Motor Mechanic-100

Description

Latest CentralGovernment Jobs for Diploma holders have been published by Northern Coalfields Ltd. for Apprentice vacancies in Uttar Pradesh. If you are searching for a government job in Uttar Pradesh then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Apprentice, from 10-06-2021, and till 09-07-2021 till 05:00 PM. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Uttar Pradesh and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for Apprentice vacancies in Uttar Pradesh, your ITI diploma must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 10-06-2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these posts is 09-07-2021 till 05:00 PM

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 16 to 24  years old. 

Northern Coalfields Ltd. Apprentice Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Uttar Pradesh Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is 12000.

How to apply for Northern Coalfields Ltd. Apprentice Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Apprentice. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of Northern Coalfields Ltd. and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by Northern Coalfields Ltd.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
